          "id": "NARR_INTRO",
          "type": "npc_line",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "The hallway smells like paper and warm dust. (pause)\nA door labeled RECORDS sits flush in a steel frame. (pause)\nIt\u2019s the kind that assumes you\u2019ll stop asking. (pause)\nTo its right: a pneumatic tube station with a yellowed instruction card. (pause)\nBelow a fire panel: a taped note with too many initials. (pause)\nA wall placard explains faxing like it\u2019s hazardous waste.",
          "next": "MAIN_MENU"
        },
        {
          "id": "MAIN_MENU",
          "type": "player_choice",
          "speakerId": "PLAYER",
          "text": "What do I check?",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "ASK_SUMMARIZE",
              "text": "(ask) Summarize and log the situation.",
              "next": "COMMIT_PROMPT"
            },
            {
