        },
        {
          "id": "COMMIT_NARR1",
          "type": "npc_line",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "You have enough to say later (pause) that you tried the obvious door first. (pause)\nThe hallway offers two acceptable alternatives: (pause) send the request like cargo (pause) or escalate it like smoke. (pause)\nNeither requires anyone to admit (pause) they gave you access.",
